quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  24,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  24,1,"yeh aik sourat hai jis ko hum ne nazil kya hai, aur usay hum ne farz kya hai, aur is mein hum ne saaf saaf Hadayat nazil ki hain, shayad ke tum sabaq lau"
  24,2,"zania aurat aur zaani mard, dono mein se har aik ko so korray maro aur un par taras khanay ka jazba Allah ke deen ke muamlay mein tum ko daman geer nah ho agar tum Allah taala aur roz aakhir par imaan rakhtay ho aur un ko saza dete waqt ahal imaan ka aik giroh mojood rahay"
  24,3,zaani nikah nah kere magar zania ke sath ya mshrk_h ke sath aur zania ke sath nikah nah kere magar zaani ya mushriq aur yeh haraam kar diya gaya hai ahal imaan par
  24,4,"aur jo log pak daman aurton par tohmat lagayen, phir chaar gawah le kar nah ayen, un ko isi korray maro aur un ki shahadat kabhi qubool nah karo, aur woh khud hi fasik hain"
  24,5,siwaye unn logon ke jo is harkat ke baad Taib ho jayen aur islaah kar len ke Allah zaroor ( unn ke haq mein ) ghafoor o Raheem hai
  24,6,aur jo log apni biwion par ilzaam lagayen aur un ke paas khud un ke apne siwa dosray koi gawah nah hon to unn mein seshakhs ki shahadat ( yeh hai ke woh ) chaar martaba Allah ki qasam kha kar gawahi day ke woh ( apne ilzaam mein ) sacha hai
  24,7,aur panchwin baar kahe ke uss par Allah ki laanat ho agar woh ( apne ilzaam mein ) jhoota ho
  24,8,aur aurat se saza is terhan tal sakti hai ke woh chaar martaba Allah ki qasam kha kar shahadat day ke yeh shakhs ( apne ilzaam mein ) jhoota hai
  24,9,aur panchwin martaba kahe ke uss bandi par Allah ka ghazab tootay agar woh ( apne ilzaam mein ) sacha ho
  24,10,"tum logon par Allah ka fazl aur is ka reham nah hota aur yeh baat nah hoti ke Allah bara iltifaat frmane wala aur hakeem hai, to ( biwion par ilzaam ka maamla tumhe barri paicheedgi mein daal deta )"
  24,11,jo log yeh bohtan ghurr laaye hain woh tumahray hi andar ka aik tolh hain is waqeye ko apne haq mein shar nah samjhoo balkay yeh bhi tumahray liye kher hi hai jis ne is mein jitna hissa liya is ne itna hi gunah sameta aur jis shakhs ne iss ki zimma daari ka bara hissa apne sir liya is ke liye to azaab azeem hai
  24,12,jis waqt tum logon ne usay suna tha usi waqt kyun nah momin mardon aur momin aurton ne apne aap se naik gumaan kya aur kyun nah keh diya ke yeh Sarih bohtan hai ?
  24,13,"woh log ( apne ilzaam ke saboot mein ) chaar gawah kyun nah laaye? ab ke woh gawah nahi laaye hain, Allah ke nazdeek wohi jhutay hain"
  24,14,agar tum logon par duniya aur akhirat mein Allah ka fazl aur reham o karam nah hota to jin baton mein tum par gay thay un ki Padaash mein bara azaab tumhe aa laita
  24,15,"( zara ghhor to karo, uss waqt tum kaisi sakht ghalti kar rahay thay ) jabkay tumhari aik zabaan se doosri zabaan is jhoot ko layte ja rahi thi aur tum apne mun se woh kuch kahe ja rahay thay jis ke mutaliq tumhe koi ilm nah tha tum usay aik mamooli baat samajh rahay thay, halaank Allah ke nazdeek yeh barri baat thi"
  24,16,"kyun nah ussay suntay hi tum ne keh diya ke"" hamein aisi baat zabaan se nikalna Zaib nahi deta, subhan Allah , yeh to aik bohtan azeem hai """
  24,17,Allah tum ko nasiyaat karta hai ke aindah kabhi aisi harkat nah karna agar tum momin ho
  24,18,Allah tumhe saaf saaf Hadayat deta hai aur woh Aleem o hakeem hai
  24,19,"jo log chahtay hain ke imaan laane walon ke giroh mein fehash phailay woh duniya aur akhirat mein dard naak saza ke mustahiq hain, Allah jaanta hai aur tum nahi jantay"
  24,20,agar Allah ka fazl aur is ka reham o karam tum par nah hota aur yeh baat nah hoti ke Allah bara shafeeq o Raheem hai ( to yeh cheez jo abhi tumahray andar phailai gayi thi bad tareen nataij dikha deti )
  24,21,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, shetan ke naqsh qadam par nah chalo is ki pairwi koi kere ga to woh usay fehash aur badi hi ka hukum day ga agar Allah ka fazl aur is ka reham o karam tum par nah hota to tum mein se koi shakhs pak nah ho sakta magar Allah hi jisay chahta hai pak kar deta hai, aur Allah suneney wala aur jan-nay wala hai"
  24,22,"tum mein se jo log sahib fazl aur sahib mqdrt hain woh is baat ki qasam nah kha bathain ke apne rishta daar, maskeen aur mohajir fi Sabeel Allah logon ki madad nah karen ge inhen maaf kar dena chahiye aur dar guzar karna chahiye kya tum nahi chahtay ke Allah tumhe maaf kere? aur Allah ki sift yeh hai ke woh ghafoor aur Raheem hai"
  24,23,"jo log pak daman, be khabar, momin aurton par tohmatain lagatay hain un par duniya aur akhirat mein laanat ki gayi aur un ke liye bara azaab hai"
  24,24,woh is din ko bhool nah jayen jabkay un ki apni zubanain aur un ke apne haath paon un ke krtoton ki gawahi den ge
  24,25,is din Allah woh badla inhen bharpoor day ga jis ke woh mustahiq hain aur inhen maloom ho jaye ga ke Allah hi haq hai sach ko sach kar dikhaane wala
  24,26,"khabees aurtain khabees mardon ke liye hain aur khabees mard khabees aurton ke liye pakeeza aurtain pakeeza mardon ke liye hain aur pakeeza mard pakeeza aurton ke liye un ka daman pak hai unn baton se jo bananay walay banatay hain, un ke liye mughfirat hai aur rizaq kareem"
  24,27,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, apne gharon ke siwa dosray gharon mein daakhil nah howa karo jab taq ke ghar walon ki Raza nah le lau aur ghar walon par salam nah bhaij lau, yeh tareeqa tumahray liye behtar hai tawaqqa hai ke tum is ka khayaal rakho ge"
  24,28,"phir agar wahan kisi ko nah pao to daakhil nah ho jab taq ke tum ko ijazat nah day di jaye, aur agar tum se kaha jaye ke wapas chalay jao to wapas ho jao, yeh tumahray liye ziyada pakeeza tareeqa hai, aur jo kuch tum karte ho Allah usay khoob jaanta hai"
  24,29,"Albata tumahray liye is mein koi muzahiqa nahi hai ke aisay gharon mein daakhil ho jao jo kisi ke rehne ki jagah nah hon aur jin mein tumahray faiday ( ya kaam ) ki koi cheez ho, tum jo kuch zahir karte ho aur jo kuch chupatay ho sab ki Allah ko khabar hai"
  24,30,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, momin mardon se kaho ke apni nazrain bacha kar rakhen aur apni sharamgahon ki hifazat karen, yeh unn ke liye ziyada pakeeza tareeqa hai, jo kuch woh karte hain Allah uss se bakhabar rehta hai"
  24,31,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, momin aurton se keh do ke apni nazrain bacha kar rakhen, aur apni sharamgahon ki hifazat karen, aur apna banaao singhar nah deikhein bajuz uss ke jo khud zahir ho jaye, aur apne seenon par apni orrnihon ke aanchal daaley rahen woh apna banaao singhar nah zahir karen magar inn logon ke samnay : shohar, baap, shohron ke baap, apne betay, shohron ke betay, bhai, bhaiyon ke betay, behnoon ke betay, apne mil jol ki aurtain, apannay mamlook, woh zair dast mard jo kisi aur qisam ki gharz nah rakhtay hon, aur woh bachay jo aurton ki posheeda baton se abhi waaqif nah hue hon woh a pannay paon zameen par martii hui nah chala karen ke apni jo zeenat unhon ne chhupa rakhi ho is ka logon ko ilm ho jaye ae momino, tum sab mil kar Allah se tauba karo, tawaqqa hai ke Falah pao ge"
  24,32,"tum mein se jo log mujarad hon, aur tumahray londi ghulamoo mein se jo Saleh hon, un ke nikah kar do agar woh ghareeb hon to Allah apne fazl se unn ko ghanni kar day ga, Allah barri wusat wala aur Aleem hai"
  24,33,"aur jo nikah ka mauqa nah payen inhen chahiye ke Iffat mabi ikhtiyar karen, yahan taq ke Allah apne fazl se unn ko ghanni kar day aur tumahray mamlokon mein se jo maktbatki darkhwast karen un se makatbatkar lau agar tumhe maloom ho ke un ke andar bhalai hai, aur un ko uss maal mein se do jo Allah ne tumhe diya hai aur apni londion ko a pannay dunewi faido ki khatir qahba giri par majaboor nah karo jabkay woh khud Pakdaman rehna chahti hon, aur jo koi unn ko majaboor kere to iss jabar ke baad Allah unn ke liye ghafoor o Raheem hai"
  24,34,"hum ne saaf saaf hadaayat dainay wali ayaat tumahray paas bhaij di hain, aur un qomon ki abratnak misalein bhi hum tumahray samnay paish kar chuke hain jo tum se pehlay ho guzri hain, aur woh nsihtin hum ne kar di hain jo darny walon ke liye hoti hain"
  24,35,"Allah asmano aur zameen ka noor hai ( kaayenaat mein ) is ke noor ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aik taaq mein chairag rakha howa ho, chairag aik fanoos mein ho, fanoos ka haal yeh ho ke jaisay moti ki terhan chamakta howa tara, aur woh chairag Zaitoon ke aik aisay mubarak darakht ke tail se roshan kya jata ho jo Sharqi ho nah ghrbi, jis ka tail aap hi aap bahrakna parta ho chahay aag is ko nah lagey, ( iss terhan ) roshni par roshni ( bherne ke tamam asbaab jama ho gay hon ) Allah apne noor ki taraf jis ki chahta hai rahnumai farmata hai, woh logon ko misalon se baat samajhata hai, woh har cheez se khoob waaqif hai"
  24,36,"( uss ke noor ki taraf hadaayat panay walay ) unn gharon mein paye jatay hain jinhein buland karne ka, aur jin mein apne naam ki yaad ka Allah ne azan diya hai"
  24,37,unn mein aisay log subah o shaam uss ki tasbeeh karte hain jinhein tijarat aur khareed o farokht Allah ki yaad se aur Iqamat namaz o adaye zkoh se ghaafil nahi kar deti woh uss din se drtay rehtay hain jis mein dil ulatnay aur daiday pathra jaane ki nobat aa jaye gi
  24,38,"( aur woh yeh sab kuch is liye karte hain ) taakay Allah un ke behtareen aamaal ki jaza unn ko day aur mazeed apne fazl se nawaze, Allah jisay chahta hai be hisaab deta hai"
  24,39,"( is ke bar aks ) jinhon ne kufar kya un ke aamaal ki misaal aisi hai jaisay dasht be aabb mein saraab ke piyasa uss ko pani samjhay hue tha, magar jab wahan pouncha to kuch nah paaya, balkay wahan is ne Allah ko mojood paaya, jis ne is ka poora poora hisaab chuka diya, aur Allah ko hisaab letay der nahi lagti"
  24,40,"ya phir is ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aik gehray samandar mein andhera, ke oopar aik mouj chhai hui hai, uss par aik aur mouj, aur is ke oopar baadal, tareqi par tareqi musallat hai, aadmi apna haath nikalay to usay bhi nah dekhnay paye jisay Allah noor nah bakhshay uss ke liye phir koi noor nahi"
  24,41,"kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah ki tasbeeh kar rahay hain woh sab jo asmano aur zameen mein hain aur woh parinday jo par phela ye urr rahay hain? har aik apni namaz aur tasbeeh ka tareeqa jaanta hai, aur yeh sab jo kuch karte hain Allah is se bakhabar rehta hai"
  24,42,asmano aur zameen ki badshahi Allah hi ke liye hai aur isi ki taraf sab ko palatna hai
  24,43,"kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah baadal ko aahista aahista chalata hai, phir is ke tukron ko baahum jorta hai, phir usay samaitt kar aik kaseef abr bana deta hai, phir tum dekhte ho ke is ke khoal mein se barish ke qatray tpkte chalay atay hain aur woh aasman se, unn pahoron ki badolat jo is mein buland hain, olley barsata hai, phir jisay chahta hai un ka nuqsaan pohanchata hai aur jisay chahta hai un se bacha laita hai uss ki bijli ki chamak nigahon ko Khaira kiye deti hai"
  24,44,raat aur din ka ulat phair wohi kar raha hai iss mein aik sabaq hai aankhon walon ke liye
  24,45,"aur Allah ne har jandaar aik terhan ke pani se peda kya, koi pait ke bil chal raha hai to koi do tangon par aur koi chaar tangon par jo kuch woh chahta hai peda karta hai, woh har cheez par Qadir hai"
  24,46,"hum ne saaf saaf haqeeqat bitanay wali ayaat nazil kar di hain, agay Siraat mustaqeem ki taraf hadaayat Allah hi jisay chahta hai deta hai"
  24,47,"yeh log kehte hain ke hum imaan laaye Allah aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam par aur hum ne itaat qubool ki, magar is ke baad un mein se aik giroh ( itaat se ) mun mourr jata hai aisay log hargiz momin nahi hain"
  24,48,"jab un ko bulaya jata hai Allah aur rasool ki taraf, taakay rasool un ke aapas ke muqadmay ka faisla kere to un mein se aik fareeq katra jata hai"
  24,49,Albata agar haq un ki muwafiqat mein ho to rasool ke paas barray itaat kish ban kar aa jatay hain
  24,50,kya un ke dilon ko ( munafqat ka ) rog laga howa hai? ya yeh shak mein parre hue hain? ya un ko yeh khauf hai ke Allah aur is ka rasool un par zulm kere ga? asal baat yeh hai ke zalim to yeh log khud hain
  24,51,imaan laane walon ka kaam to yeh hai ke jab woh Allah aur rasool ki taraf bulaa ye jayen taakay rasool un ke muqadmay ka faisla kere to woh kahin ke hum ne suna aur itaat ki aisay hi log Falah panay walay hain
  24,52,aur kamyaab wohi hain jo Allah aur rasool ki farmaa bardari karen aur Allah se dareen aur is ki nafarmani se bachchen
  24,53,"yeh ( munafiq ) Allah ke naam se kari kari kasmain kha kar kehte hain ke"" aap hukum den to hum gharon se nikal kharray hon"" inn se kaho"" kasmain nah khao, tumhari itaat ka haal maloom hai, tumahray krtoton se Allah be khabar nahi hai """
  24,54,"kaho,"" Allah ke Mutee bano aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke tabay farmaan ban kar raho lekin agar tum mun phertey ho to khoob samajh lau ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam par jis farz ka baar rakha gaya hai uss ka zimma daar woh hai aur tum par jis farz ka baar dala gaya hai uss ke zimma daar tum ho uss ki itaat karo ge to khud hi hadaayat pao ge warna rasool ki zimma daari is se ziyada kuch nahi hai ke saaf saaf hukum pouncha day """
  24,55,"Allah ne wada farmaya hai tum mein se unn logon ke sath jo imaan layein aur naik amal karen ke woh un ko usi terhan zameen mein khalifa banaye ga jis terhan unn se pehlay guzray hue logon ko bana chuka hai, unn ke liye unn ke uss deen ko mazboot bunyadon par qaim kar day ga jisay Allah taala ne unn ke haq mein pasand kya hai, aur unn ki ( mojooda ) haalat khauf ko aman se badal day ga, bas woh meri bandagi karen aur mere sath kisi ko shareek nah karen aur jo is ke baad kufar kere to aisay hi log fasik hain"
  24,56,"namaz qaim karo, zkoh do, aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki itaat karo, umeed hai ke tum par reham kya jaye ga"
  24,57,jo log kufar kar rahay hain a noon ke mutaliq is ghalat fehmi mein nah raho ke woh zameen mein Allah ko aajiz kar den ge un ka thikana dozakh hai aur woh bara hi bura thikana hai
  24,58,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, lazim hai ke tumahray mamlook aur tumahray woh bachay jo abhi aqal ki hadd ko nahi puhanche hain, teen auqaat mein ijazat le kar tumahray paas aaya karen : subah ki namaz se pehlay, aur dopehar ko jabkay tum kapray utaar kar rakh dete ho, aur esha ki namaz ke baad yeh teen waqt tumahray liye parday ke waqt hain inn ke baad woh bulaa ijazat ayen to nah tum par koi gunah hai nah unn par, tumhe aik dosray ke paas baar baar aana hi hota hai is terhan Allah tumahray liye apne arshadat ki tozeeh karta hai, aur woh Aleem o hakeem hai"
  24,59,"aur jab tumahray bachay aqal ki hadd ko poanch jayen to chahay ke usi terhan ijazat leker aaya karen jis terhan unn ke barray ijazat letay rahay hain iss terhan Allah apni ayaat tumahray samnay kholta hai, aur woh Aleem o hakeem hai"
  24,60,"aur jo aurtain jawani se guzri baithi hon, nikah ki umeed waar nah hon, woh agar apni chadrin utaar kar rakh den to unn par koi gunah nahi, bashart e kay zeenat ki numaish karne wali nah hon taham woh bhi hyadari hi barten to unn ke haq mein acha hai, aur Allah sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
  24,61,"koi harj nahi agar koi andha, ya langra, ya mareez ( kisi ke ghar se kha le ) aur nah tumahray oopar iss mein koi muzahiqa hai ke apne gharon se khao ya apne baap dada ke gharon se, ya apni maa nani ke gharon se, ya apne bhaiyon ke gharon se, ya apni behnoon ke gharon se, ya apne chchaon ke gharon se, ya apni phophiyun ke gharon se, ya apne mamo-on ke gharon se, ya apni khala-on ke gharon se, ya unn gharon se jin ki knjyan tumhari supurdagi mein hon, ya apne doston ke gharon se is mein bhi koi harj nahi ke tum log mil kar khao ya allag allag Albata jab gharon mein daakhil howa karo to apne logon ko salam kya karo, dua ye kher, Allah ki taraf se muqarrar fir maai hui, barri babarkat aur pakeeza iss terhan Allah taala tumahray samnay ayaat bayan karta hai, tawaqqa hai ke tum samajh boojh se kaam lau ge"
  24,62,"momin to asal mein wohi hain jo Allah aur uss ke rasool ko dil se manen aur jab kisi ijtimai kaam ke mauqa par Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke sath hon to uss se ijazat liye baghair nah jayen jo log tum se ijazat mangte hain wohi Allah aur rasool ke maan-ne walay hain, pas jab woh apne kisi kaam se ijazat mangeen to jisay tum chaho ijazat day diya karo aur aisay logon ke haq mein Allah se duaye mughfirat kya karo, Allah yaqeenan ghafoor o Raheem hai"
  24,63,"musalmano, apne darmain Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke bulanay ko aapas mein aik dosray ka sa bulana nah samajh betho Allah unn logon ko khoob jaanta hai jo tum mein aisay hain ke aik dosray ki aarr letay hue chupkay se stk jatay hain Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke hukum ki khilaaf warzi karne walon ko darna chahiye ke woh kisi ftne mein girftar nah ho jayen ya un par dard naak azaab nah aa jaye"
  24,64,"khabardaar raho, aasman o zameen mein jo kuch hai Allah ka hai tum jis rawish par bhi ho Allah uss ko jaanta hai jis roz log uss ki taraf پلٹیں ge woh unhen bta day ga ke woh kya kuch kar ke aeye hain woh har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai"
